          <p>The user can press a button to toggle the Table of Contents and page content to fill the entire screen.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Next &amp; Previous Pages</h4>
          <p>You can ask Doctasm to display special links to take you to the next and previous pages.</p>
